            <ul><li><b>Defination:</b>A goal is a desired result or purpose that a person or group commits to achieving.</li>
            <li><b>Purpose:</b>Goal setting provides long-term vision and short-term motivation. It helps organize time and resources.</li>
        <li><b>The "Why":</b> Without a clear goal, effort is diffused and progress is difficult to measure. </li>
        <li><h4>Defining SMART Goals:</h4>
        
                <li><b>Specifioc:</b>Clear, detailed, and simple (What do I want to accomplish?)</li>
                <li><b>Achievable:Realistic and "do-able" within a reasonable time frame</b></li>
